data.description: This 3 year old home is located in the Carmell Ridge Subdivision and has been beautifully maintened! Convenient to shopping, restaurants, & Downtown Milton!  This 3 bed 2 bath patio home features a trey ceiling in the living room with wood laminate floor. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining and comes with stainless steel appliances and overlooks the formal dining room. Master suite also features trey ceilings, a walk in closet, and double vanity. Two additional well sized bedrooms are located towards the front of the home. Home has a privacy fenced in backyard and double driveway for parking! Schedule a tour of this home now as it won't last long!
